> <4> [197.116939]
> but task is already holding lock:
> <4> [197.122730] ffff88811b772a40 (&hwmon->hwmon_lock){+.+.}-{3:3}, at: hwm_energy+0x4b/0x100 [i915]
> <4> [197.131543]
